backup_data.description:
The JSON backup string containing the accounts to import. Example:

{
    "timestamp": "2025-06-03T17:18:55.123Z",
    "accounts": [
        {
            "address": "0x123...",
            "private_key": "0x456...",
            "aes_key": "0x789...",
            "is_default": true
        },
        ...
    ]
}
